  <description type="morphology">Plants ± greenish, mostly 3–9 cm. Leaves cauline, largest 6–12(–14) × 3–5(–6) mm; blades ± round, ± densely lanuginose. Heads: longest 3–3.7 mm. Pistillate paleae 2.5–3.7 mm. Cypselae mostly 1–1.7 mm.</description>
